@startuml

actor User
participant "Django View" as View
participant "Django Form" as Form
participant "Django Model" as Model
participant "Azure Face API" as AzureAPI
participant "Email Service" as Email

User -> View : Submit missing person report
View -> Form : Validate form data
Form --> View : Validation result
View -> Model : Create MissingPerson
Model --> View : MissingPerson instance
View -> AzureAPI : Generate face ID
AzureAPI --> View : Face ID
View -> Model : Update MissingPerson with face ID
Model --> View : Updated MissingPerson
View -> User : Display success message

User -> View : Submit found person report
View -> Form : Validate form data
Form --> View : Validation result
View -> Model : Create ReportedPerson
Model --> View : ReportedPerson instance
View -> AzureAPI : Generate face ID
AzureAPI --> View : Face ID
View -> Model : Update ReportedPerson with face ID
Model --> View : Updated ReportedPerson
View -> AzureAPI : Check for potential matches
AzureAPI --> View : Matching results
alt Potential match found
    View -> Model : Update MissingPerson with lead
    Model --> View : Updated MissingPerson
    View -> Email : Send notification to contact person
    Email --> View : Notification sent confirmation
end
View -> User : Display success message

@enduml